        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>ALS Placebo No More Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Food and Drug Administration and the National Institutes of Health to collaborate to provide all patients with ALS (amyotrophic lateral sclerosis,&nbsp;also referred to as Lou Gehrig's disease) with access to medicines in clinical trials.</p>]]></text>
